<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:In the provided project configuration HAVE_SENDMSG is defined (and thus the #ifdef HAVE_SENDMSG branch is taken) while MHD_WINSOCK_SOCKETS is not defined. The Windows-specific WSASend block is under #elif defined(MHD_WINSOCK_SOCKETS) and therefore will never be compiled or executed in this configuration, making that fragment unreachable.
</scenario>
